room_title: Escape room "Specimen" by Puzzah! in Denver
room_address: FlatIron Crossing, 1 W Flatiron Circle #2153 Broomfield, CO 80021
room_description: You wake up and find yourselves trapped in a dark holding cell. The technology in the cell is highly advanced and the furnishings are otherworldly. You're not sure how you got here, but you've heard crazy stories about alien abductions. Are you specimens on an alien ship? Can you get back to Earth?
